Support Vector Machine
Decision Tree
🔷 Real World Uses of Supervised Learning
Fraud Detection

Banks use ML to detect suspicious transactions.

Medical Diagnosis

Predict diseases using patient data.

Example:

diabetes prediction
cancer detection
heart disease risk
Salary Prediction

Companies estimate salary based on:

experience
skills
location
